Hi @Swastyy 
Thank you for your contribution, I have some suggestions:
1. Do not use uppercase for the name of the directory, you can refer to other directories;
2. There should be some content in `_index_*.md`, please refer to https://github.com/apache/shardingsphere/blob/master/docs/document/content/user-manual/_index.en.md;
3. `_index_*.md` of `FAQ` has been moved to the lower-level directory, so the chapter number in the file header should be changed to 7.1;
4. The new directory `others` should also contain the description files `_index.cn.md` & `_index.en.md`.

